default5.8
default              
defaultA more radical examination of alternative funding streams was presented by the London Finance Commission i
defaultn its 
defaultMay 2013 report, ‘Raising the Capital’
default.
default 
default 
defaultThe 
defaultCommission put forward a case for fewer borrowing constraints and greater devolved tax powers for London, which would 
defaultenable 
